Actions.Text: AMEND (T) AND RECOMMIT TO HIGHER EDUCATION

Title: Relates to the dispensing of self-administered hormonal contraceptives
Summary: Relates to the dispensing of self-administered hormonal contraceptives; authorizes a licensed physician and a certified nurse practitioner to prescribe and order a non-patient specific regimen to a pharmacist licensed and located in the state for the dispensing of self-administered hormonal contraceptives.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the education law, in relation to the dispensing of self-administered hormonal contraceptives
